'From Squeak3.7 of ''4 September 2004'' [latest update: #5989] on 6 November 2008 at 8:37:07 am'!"Change Set:		removeControllerDate:			6 November 2008Author:			Juan VuletichAfter replacing all references to the Controller hierarchy, remove it.Make sure no instances are left!!"(nil confirm: 'Prior to continuing, check that after references to Controller have been removed, all Windows were closed, as the Controller hierarchy will be removed') ifTrue: [	Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #OldTextMorphEditor.	Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #ParagraphEditor.	Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #ScrollController.	Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #MouseMenuController.	Smalltalk removeClassNamed: #Controller ]!